    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Battlewrights</strong> is a hilarious local multiplayer combat game for two to four players. The core mechanics are deceptively simple: Press button to throw your weapon, press it again to magically recall it. Repeat until you are the last person standing. Everyone can play. Every character plays the same. But if you want to take things further, try throwjumps, charged throws, perfect throws, self-evades and game-changing powerups.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Gameplay</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112470/extras/ba78b9f1da82b590798dcc0b5f2dd9fa.poster.avif?t=1770586308\" width=1280 height=720 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112470/extras/ba78b9f1da82b590798dcc0b5f2dd9fa.webm?t=1770586308\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112470/extras/ba78b9f1da82b590798dcc0b5f2dd9fa.mp4?t=1770586308\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you throw your weapon mid-air, it lets you do something called a throwjump. Combine this move with walljumps and no platform is too high to reach!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112470/extras/0424f7ff95af08190f547e62e5b40567.poster.avif?t=1770586308\" width=1280 height=720 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112470/extras/0424f7ff95af08190f547e62e5b40567.webm?t=1770586308\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112470/extras/0424f7ff95af08190f547e62e5b40567.mp4?t=1770586308\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can also dodge your ene... friends projectiles by pressing the dodge button shortly before being hit. This opens up perfect opportunities to strike back!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112470/extras/e41b7aba8bb2df01ee6b93666bda560d.poster.avif?t=1770586308\" width=1280 height=720 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112470/extras/e41b7aba8bb2df01ee6b93666bda560d.webm?t=1770586308\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112470/extras/e41b7aba8bb2df01ee6b93666bda560d.mp4?t=1770586308\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you really want to hone your movement skills, try the included time trial mode. Try to beat bronze, silver and gold times, or even dare challenging the coveted developer medal!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112470/extras/5422759feca814f867d339e1822e3d3a.poster.avif?t=1770586308\" width=1280 height=720 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112470/extras/5422759feca814f867d339e1822e3d3a.webm?t=1770586308\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112470/extras/5422759feca814f867d339e1822e3d3a.mp4?t=1770586308\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pick from 4 different characters, each with 4 different color schemes!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112470/extras/7b47e0c18c01ee47f0eaa4a95c342ef8.poster.avif?t=1770586308\" width=240 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112470/extras/7b47e0c18c01ee47f0eaa4a95c342ef8.webm?t=1770586308\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112470/extras/3872b1917ee7a0da3091f99befc90c6e.poster.avif?t=1770586308\" width=240 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112470/extras/3872b1917ee7a0da3091f99befc90c6e.webm?t=1770586308\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112470/extras/5914e877aa8e0967db8bbb430e89c53a.poster.avif?t=1770586308\" width=240 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112470/extras/5914e877aa8e0967db8bbb430e89c53a.webm?t=1770586308\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112470/extras/ab64f608a1d13e3fc04a105da9e0741b.poster.avif?t=1770586308\" width=240 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112470/extras/ab64f608a1d13e3fc04a105da9e0741b.webm?t=1770586308\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>Features</strong></u></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 4-player couch multiplayer</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Online Multiplayer through Steam Remote Play!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4 playable characters with 4 palettes each! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 4 different level-sets with their own setting, powerups and interactive elements!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 40 different levels in total!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Singleplayer time trial mode with an additional 40 levels (10 available on launch)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Leaderboards</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Handcrafted pixelart</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A pumping chiptune soundtrack</p></li></ul>",
